## Commits

- Never add `Co-authored-by: Cursor` (or any Cursor/agent co-author trailer) to commit messages.
- Write commit messages in the repo's existing style; focus on why, not a file list.

## Research

- Use web search when a question needs current docs, API behavior, browser support, CVEs, or other facts that may have changed since training data.
